\": \"I am slurring my words.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my words\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can barely speak.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both times I was tested for a stroke because I literally could not move my body.\\\"\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stroke\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She revealed that when she was first hospitalized, her doctors had \\\"absolutely no idea\\\" what her condition was and noted how \\\"scary\\\" it was to be surrounded by doctors due to her past abuse she experienced at the hands of a doctor.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her doctors\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"absolutely no idea\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"her condition\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"doctors\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"her past abuse\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"a doctor\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in 2017, she and dozens of other gymnasts came forward to exposeU.S.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"other gymnasts\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"gymnastics doctor Larry Nassarof sexual abuse.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics doctor\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"Larry Nassarof sexual abuse\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later plead guilty to numerous charges of criminal sexual conduct and in 2018 he was sentenced to 175 ye